text: The Yamalo-Nenets Autonomous Okrug (YaNAO; , ; , ) or Yamalia () is a federal subject of Russia and an autonomous okrug of Tyumen Oblast. Its administrative center is the town of Salekhard and its largest city is Noyabrsk. In 2010, 522,904 people lived there. Geography: The Yamal peninsula has some large holes in the ground that are called gas emissions crater. == References == Category:Autonomous okrugs of Russia Category:Tyumen Oblast
